title: ARMY OF THE DEAD Ending Explained & Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment:
What say we? Does ARMY OF THE DEAD get the 👍 or 👎?

Check out my Zack Snyder Justice League Differences video: https://youtu.be/Vm2btfs8lO4
Or my Horror Playlist: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7i5oOjx21bz-hnkmbeCmU4j
Kate’s whole purpose was to go save that mother. The mother didn’t even make it in the end. Kate got the rest of the crew killed if you think about it. Her character annoyed me. 😒
Chambers raised her hand up when they were asking who never killed a zombie, and then her fight scene was straight up badass, dual wielding a knife and a gun lmao
Nobody talks about Guzman? He's underrated here. He looked like a traitor in the first but he is very true to his commitment.
Chamber’s was a fricking queen! She admitted that she had never killed any zombies before and still went out like a champ
